Active Directory Performance Metrics

Added metrics for critical Active Directory components:

Netlogon: Monitors for authentication bottlenecks with metrics like semaphore_waiters and semaphore_holders.

Security: Tracks the rate of ntlm_authentications and kerberos_authentications.

DHCP Failover: Monitors the health of DHCP failover relationships.

DFS Replication: Provides visibility into SYSVOL health with metrics for staging_folder_size and conflict_files_size.

Core NTDS: Expanded to include ldap.writes_persec and ldap.active_threads.